txt.en: 'Are you looking to be welcomed into the inner circle of the Rangers of Esteldín? I can help you with that and make you \qKindred\q to the Rangers of Esteldín.\n\n'If this sounds good to you, speak to me again!'
'Alright, soon you will be Kindred to the Rangers of Esteldín. Ready?'
North Downs - Rangers of Esteldín IV
By completing this quest, you will be considered Kindred to the Rangers of Esteldín.
